All Classes

Class Description
App
The main app class, launched upon starting application
ErrorAlert
The class used to display alert message box
JsonReader
The class used to read JSON object
Key
The class used to store Google Maps API key
Location
An entity class, used to represent a location
mainUI
The main page scene of the UI, it is the first scene shown when launching the application Consists of entries for user to input start and end location addresses Switch to profileUI scene when Profile button is pressed Switch to routeUI scene when Get route button is pressed
PM25API
The class used to interface with PM2.5 API
Profile
An entity class, used to represent a user profile
Profile.Health
An enumeration containing the health conditions
ProfileManager
A class used to manage the user profile Used to get the user profile and save the user profile
profileUI
The scene displayed when user presses the Profile button in the mainUI Used to display user profile and settings (preferences) Save user's profile when user presses Save button Switch to mainUI scene when back button is pressed
PSIAPI
The class used to interface with PSI API
RequestError
An exception class, thrown when classes failed to request information from APIs An alert message box will appear when this error is thrown
RouteManager
A class used to interface with the GoogleMaps Geocoding API Used to query the location entered by users, create Location object for the corresponding location
routeUI
The scene displayed when user presses the Get route button in the mainUI Used to display route information, weather information, warnings and recommendations Switch to mainUI scene when back button is pressed
ShowWeatherInfo
A class used to format the style of the weather information text and recommendation text to be displayed on routeUI
UVIAPI
The class used to interface with UVI API
WarningLogic
The logic to determine suitable warnings and recommendations to be given to users based on the current weather condition
WeatherAPI
The class used to interface with Weather API
WeatherInfo
An entity class, used to represent weather information
WeatherInfo.Weather
Enumeration of types of weather
WeatherManager
A class used to get weather information from various APIs Uses facade design pattern, which uses different API package classes
